{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","text":"NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lef